<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Privacy Policy - BroqInsta Zero-Log Ethics</title>
    <meta name="robots" content="index, follow">
    <meta name="description" content="BroqInsta privacy policy - zero-log protocol, data security, and cookie usage.">
    <link rel="canonical" href="<%= siteUrl %>/privacy">
    <meta property="og:type" content="website">
    <meta property="og:title" content="Privacy Policy - BroqInsta Zero-Log Ethics">
    <meta property="og:description" content="BroqInsta privacy policy - zero-log protocol, data security, and cookie usage.">
    <meta property="og:image" content="<%= siteUrl %>/images/preview.png">
    <meta property="og:url" content="<%= siteUrl %>/privacy">
    <meta property="og:site_name" content="BroqInsta">
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image">
    <meta name="twitter:title" content="Privacy Policy - BroqInsta Zero-Log Ethics">
    <meta name="twitter:description" content="BroqInsta privacy policy - zero-log protocol, data security, and cookie usage.">
    <meta name="twitter:image" content="<%= siteUrl %>/images/preview.png">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <script src="/js/tailwind.js"></script>
</head>

<body class="bg-[#FAFBFC] min-h-screen flex flex-col">
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <main class="flex-grow container mx-auto px-4 py-24 max-w-4xl">
        <nav class="mb-8 text-sm font-medium text-gray-400" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
            <ol class="flex items-center space-x-2" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/BreadcrumbList">
                <li itemprop="itemListElement" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem">
                    <a href="/" itemprop="item" class="hover:text-purple-600 transition-colors"><span itemprop="name">Home</span></a>
                    <meta itemprop="position" content="1">
                </li>
                <li><span class="mx-2">/</span></li>
                <li itemprop="itemListElement" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ListItem">
                    <span itemprop="name" class="text-gray-600">Privacy Policy</span>
                    <meta itemprop="position" content="2">
                </li>
            </ol>
        </nav>

        <div class="glass-card p-12 md:p-20 rounded-[3rem] animate-on-scroll">
            <h1 class="text-5xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-12 italic">Privacy Ethics.</h1>
            <div class="space-y-10 text-gray-600 font-medium leading-relaxed">
                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest text-xs">01. Zero-Log
                        Protocol</h2>
                    <p>At BroqInsta, we implement a strict zero-log policy. We do not store, track, or monitor your
                        media extraction requests. Your downloads are processed through ephemeral memory sessions that
                        are cleared every 60 seconds.</p>
                </section>
                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest text-xs">02. Data
                        Security</h2>
                    <p>All communications between your device and our extraction nodes are encrypted using 256-bit SSL
                        technology. We never share session data with third-party advertisers.</p>
                </section>
                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest text-xs">03. Cookie Usage
                    </h2>
                    <p>We use minimal, essential cookies only to manage download rate-limiting and ensure service
                        stability. We do not use tracking pixels for user profiling.</p>
                </section>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>

</html>